y. Join daily workshops. Connect with the community. Perform to the world.\n\nSubscribe for your free 7-day trial:\n- Play on official Pioneer DJ equipment\n- Learn from the masters at the Pete Tong DJ Academy.\n- Load your own music - including via Dropbox\n- Access tracks from Beatport, Monstercat, TIDAL & Soundcloud Go+\n- Join live workshops - more than 30 per week\n- Level up your skills with game mode tutorials\n- Livestream to Twitch directly from your Meta Quest\n- Join multiplayer rooms and jam together\n\nIf you decide to cancel, no worries, you can keep mixing with a free, limited version of Tribe.\n- Play with the starter decks\n- Mix up to 5 tracks per session\n- Join multiplayer sessions\n- Continue learning with the 5 day DJ challenge\nYou can always re-subscribe when you\u2019re ready.\n\nJoin the community on Discord | discord.gg/tribexr\n\nStart your DJ journey today!", "short_description": "Become a DJ! Play on official Pioneer DJ equipment. Learn from the masters at the Pete Tong DJ Academy. Join daily workshops. Connect with the community. Perform to the world.\n\nSubscribe for your free 7-day trial:\n- Play on official Pioneer DJ equipment\n- Learn from the masters at the Pete Tong DJ Academy\n- Load your own music - including via Dropbox\n- Access tracks from Beatport, Monstercat & Soundcloud Go+\n- Join live workshops & multiplayer rooms\n- Livestream to Twitch\n- Cancel anytime"}]}, "developer_name": "Tribe XR Inc", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.tribexr.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.tribexr.com/terms-of-service", "publisher_name": "Tribe XR Inc", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.tribexr.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "323450648956687"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED", "genres": ["EDUCATIONAL", "MUSI